N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 ยง 202.5 - Filings

State Regulations

The insurer shall file with the Superintendent of Insurance the scales of commissions and schedules of fees and allowances payable under this Part, including any compensation for servicing such business in the eleventh and subsequent years. Notes
